nodes.text: Fal'Orssk was a smuggler and commentator on Gundark's Gear Datalog during the early years of the New Republic. Fal'Orssk always wore stun gauntlets while on planets with strict weapons laws. Fal'Orssk also believed that slugthrowers were effective weapons because, unlike blasters, slugthrowers could be silenced. Fal'Orssk also left comments on the entries for the GLX Firelance and the VES-700 Pulse Rifle.
